---
const scenarios = [
  '上班 10 分钟提气色',
  '面试显精神',
  '约会更温柔',
  '拍照更上镜',
  '新手第一次化妆',
];
---

<section class="section" id="scenarios">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">Scenario entry</span>
      <h2>按任务做导航，不按功能堆砌页面。</h2>
      <p>当前首页结构直接对应 PRD 的任务型导航：`Discover / Try On / Tutorial / Beauty Kit / Membership`。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-cards grid-cards-3">
      {scenarios.map((scenario, index) => (
        <article class="card scenario-card">
          <span class="scenario-index">0{index + 1}</span>
          <h3>{scenario}</h3>
          <p>进入个性化方案，优先做低门槛、强结果感的妆容推荐。</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
